<bibRefCitation author="Trkov, D. &amp; Mavric, B. &amp; Orlando-Bonaca, M. &amp; Lipej, L." box="[450,646,223,249]" pageId="86" pageNumber="87" pagination="59 - 72" refId="ref65518" refString="Trkov, D., Mavric, B., Orlando-Bonaca, M. &amp; Lipej, L. (2019) Marine cryptobenthic fish fauna of Slovenia (Northern Adriatic Sea). Annales, Series Historia Naturalis, 29 (1), 59 - 72. https: // doi. org / 10.19233 / ASHN. 2019.07" type="journal article" year="2019">
Trkov 
