<bibRefCitation author="Yokes, M. B." box="[982,1119,259,286]" pageId="86" pageNumber="87" pagination="197" refId="ref51880" refString="Bilecenog ˘ lu, M. &amp; Yokes, M. B. (2016) Scuba observations reveal a wider distribution range for Thorogobius macrolepis (Teleostei: Gobiidae). Annales: Series Historia Naturalis, 26 (2), 197." type="journal article" year="2016">Yokes 2016</bibRefCitation>
